With the following steps, we can use amazon-cognito-identity-js to get the token 
from cognito

1. npm i amazon-cognito-identity-js
2. Add "browser": {
        "crypto": false
    } to package.json

3. Add "allowedCommonJsDependencies": [
        "crypto-js/lib-typedarrays",
        "crypto-js/hmac-sha256",
        "crypto-js/enc-base64",
        "crypto-js/sha256",
        "buffer",
        "js-cookie",
        "isomorphic-unfetch"
    ] to angular.json => projects => architect => build